{"word":"G2597 - καταβαίνω - katabaínō - kat-ab-ah'-ee-no - Come down","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταβαίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katabaínō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-ab-ah'-ee-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Come down</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இறங்கு, விழு"},{"paragraph":"to go down, come down, descend"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G939 - βάσις - básis - bas'-ece/939\">G939</a>; to <i>descend</i> (literally or figuratively): - come (get, go, step) down, descend, fall (down).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2597/2597\">G2597</a>, <a href=\"#/G305/305\">G305</a>, <a href=\"#/G3397/3397\">G3397</a>"}]}